title: 164: Genetics vs. Steroids
description: Can steroids give you the added edge to take you from good to great in athletics and the muscle building game? How important are genetics to these pursuits? Sal, Adam & Justin reveal just how much of an edge steroids will give you and how to maximize performance and results. Please subscribe, rate and review this show! Learn more about Mind Pump at www.mindpumpradio.com
